headline: 2 Soaring Stocks to Hold for the Next 20 Years
summary: Share prices of Amazon and Costco have risen by 94% and 115%, respectively, over the past three years.  Both companies have broad appeal to consumers and significant competitive advantages.  The stock market's recent volatility has overshadowed some of the tremendous returns that many stocks have experienced over the past several years.
